news.title: Chandigarh: If property tax not paid in 15 days, no water for 800 houses
news.para: The tax branch of the municipal corporation (MC) will start issuing notices to people who have failed to pay their property tax even after receiving recovery notices from Tuesday.

news.title: Karnataka gets nod to conduct drone survey for property ownership records in Bengaluru
news.para: ​In a statement, the ministry said the Karnataka government is one of the 10 organisations and it has got the permission to conduct "drone based aerial survey for creating urban property ownership records in Bengaluru".

news.title: East Delhi civic body adopts a resolution on sealing moratorium till March
news.para: The resolution aims to provide relief from demolition or sealing activity to such properties. Officials would also be directed to provide NOC to such properties for water and electricity connections.

news.title: Now get building permits within 30 days in Chennai
news.para: Assistant executive engineers are to make a site visit within five days of admitting the application, enter the inspection report online within the next two days and must verify documents within the next five days.

news.title: All tehsils to use GPS for mapping land: Haryana CM
news.para: Officials said many applications had been piling up at the tehsil offices and the DGPS would only fast-track the process of demarcating plots.

news.title: Noida: No nod to layouts, yet flats sold at cheap rates
news.para: The building — Dee Heights Residency — neither had any firefighting equipment, nor was its plan approved by the Noida Authority or the fire department.

news.title: Government approves construction of 16,488 more homes under PMAY-Urban
news.para: The houses approved in the meeting on Monday are proposed to be constructed under Beneficiary-Led Construction (BLC) and Affordable Housing in Partnership (AHP) verticals of PMAY-U.

news.title: Shalimar Paints posts net loss of Rs 20 crore in Q1 FY22
news.para: Revenue from operations was up 46.51 per cent at Rs 65.2 crore during the quarter under review as against Rs 44.5 crore in the year-ago period.

news.title: Tamil Nadu on massive exercise to correct mistakes in digital land records
news.para: Several land owners, even those who have modest land holding, had complained to the department that they have to wait for long hours and even several days to get the mistakes corrected in the digital records and were facing massive problems due to this.

news.title: US: Federal court set to rule on eviction moratorium this week
news.para: The judge refused landlords' request to put the Biden administration's new eviction moratorium on hold, though she ruled that the freeze is illegal.

news.title: Exxaro Tiles shares list at 5% premium
news.para: As the trade progressed, it jumped 10.25 per cent to Rs 132.30 on both the exchanges. Exxaro Tiles' initial public offering received 22.68 times subscription earlier this month.

news.title: HC asks ED to respond to Avantha Group promoter's plea challenging arrest
news.para: Thapar has approached the high court challenging a trial court's August 5 order by which his plea to declare his arrest as illegal was dismissed without recording reasons.

news.title: HDFC launches green and sustainable deposits
news.para: These deposits will carry interest rates up to 6.55 per cent while maturity period would vary from three to five years. Senior citizens (60 years+) will be eligible for an additional 0.25 per cent per annum on deposits up to Rs 2 crore.

news.title: Asking prices for houses in Britain slip in July: Rightmove
news.para: Real estate website Rightmove said asking prices fell by 0.3% in its August survey after a 0.7% increase in July, dragged down by "upper end" houses of four bedrooms or more, which saw asking prices fall by 0.8% in July.

news.title: China's new home price growth slows as speculative curbs bite
news.para: Average new home prices in China's 70 major cities rose 0.3% in July from a month earlier, slowing from a 0.5% gain in June, according to Reuters calculations based on data released by the National Bureau of Statistics (NBS).
